"  </div>",
"  <div id=\"drugCopy\">",
"   Copyright 1978-2013 Lexicomp, Inc. All rights reserved.",
"  </div>",
"  <div id=\"topicText\">",
"   (For additional information",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_general\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?5/22/5480?source=see_link\">",
